#. Tag: keyword
#: index.docbook:26
#, no-c-format
msgid "System Settings"
msgstr "Sistemaren ezarpenak"

#. Tag: keyword
#: index.docbook:27
#, no-c-format
msgid "splash screen"
msgstr "Plasta pantaila"

#. Tag: keyword
#: index.docbook:28
#, no-c-format
msgid "theme"
msgstr "gaia"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:32
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This module provides an interface to view and select splash screen themes."
msgstr ""
"Modulu horrek plasta pantailen gaiak ikusteko eta hautatzeko interfaze bat "
"ematen du."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:36
#, no-c-format
msgid "Here's a screenshot of the splash screen manager"
msgstr "Hor dago plasta pantaila kudeatzailearen pantaila-argazki bat"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:42
#, no-c-format
msgid "The splash screen manager module"
msgstr "Plasta pantaila kudeatzailearen modulua"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:48
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"On this page you can see previews of already installed splash screens. The "
"preview of the current splash screen is highlighted."
msgstr ""
"Orri honetan dagoeneko instalatuta dauden plasta pantailen aurreikuspegiak "
"ikus ditzakezu. Uneko plasta pantailaren aurreikuspegia nabarmenduta dago."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:50
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Hover a preview image with the mouse cursor then the button "
"<guilabel>Preview Splash Screen</guilabel> appears at the bottom right of "
"the image. Press this button to view the splashscreen in action."
msgstr ""
"Saguaren erakuslea aurreikuspegi irudi baten gainetik igarota, irudiaren "
"behe-eskuinean <guilabel>Aurreikusi plasta pantaila</guilabel> agertzen da. "
"Sakatu botoi hori plasta pantaila ekinean ikusteko."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:54
#, no-c-format
msgid "Get New Splash Screens..."
msgstr "Lortu Plasta pantaila berriak..."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:56
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You need to be connected to the Internet to use this action. A dialog will "
"display a list of themes from the <ulink url=\"https://store.kde.org"
"\">https://store.kde.org</ulink> website. Clicking the <guibutton>Install</"
"guibutton> button associated with a theme will install this theme locally."
msgstr ""
"Internetera konektatuta egon behar duzu ekintza hori erabiltzeko. "
"Elkarrizketa-koadro batek <ulink url=\"https://store.kde.org\">https://store."
"kde.org</ulink> webguneko gai zerrenda bat azalduko du. Gai batekin "
"elkartutako <guibutton>Instalatu</guibutton> botoia klikatzean gai hori era "
"lokalean instalatuko du."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:61
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Installing a new theme</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Gai berri bat instalatzen</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:67
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Installing a new theme</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Gai berri bat instalatzen</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:72
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This new theme is immediately available after you close the &systemsettings; "
"Download New Splash Screens dialog and is highlighted. The preview displays "
"the picture. You need to click the <guibutton>Apply</guibutton> button to "
"make this theme your current splash-screen theme."
msgstr ""
"Gai berri hori &systemsettings; Zama-jaitsi Plasta pantaila berria itxi eta "
"berehala erabilgarri dago eta nabarmenduta agertzen da. Aurreikuspegiak "
"irudia azaltzen du. <guibutton>Aplikatu</guibutton> botoian klik egin behar "
"duzu gai hori zure uneko plasta pantailako gaia egiteko."
